Formerly a [[currency_exchange]] where bitcoins were able to be purchased by those in the U.S. using a credit or debit card.  For the article about the similarly-named Bitcoin mining operation, see [[Simplecoin.us]].

The service was launched on December 4th, 2011 (1.1).  Within weeks, the service stopped functioning.

